{{ define "content" }}
<h2 style="color: #111827; font-size: 20px; line-height: 1.3; margin: 0 0 18px; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: -0.01em;">Bounce rate alert</h2>
<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">Hi {{ .UserName }},</p>

<div class="alert-box alert-danger" style="padding: 14px 16px; border-radius: 10px; margin: 20px 0; font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.55; background-color: #fef2f2; border: 1px solid #fecaca; color: #991b1b;">
  The bounce rate {{ if .WorkspaceName }}for <strong>{{ .WorkspaceName }}</strong> {{ end }}over the last 24 hours is <strong>{{ .BounceRate }}%</strong>, exceeding your {{ .Threshold }}% threshold.
</div>

<table class="stats-table" role="presentation" style="width: 100%; border-collapse: separate; border-spacing: 0; margin: 20px 0; border: 1px solid #eceef2; border-radius: 10px; overflow: hidden;">
  <tr>
    <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9fafb; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em;">Metric (24h)</th>
    <th style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9fafb; color: #6b7280; font-weight: 600; font-size: 11px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.06em; text-align: right;">Count</th>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2; font-size: 14px; color: #111827;">Total emails</td>
    <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2; font-size: 14px; color: #111827; text-align: right;">{{ .TotalEmails }}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2; font-size: 14px; color: #111827;">Bounces</td>
    <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2; font-size: 14px; color: #111827; text-align: right; color: #dc2626; font-weight: 600;">{{ .BounceCount }}</td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2; font-size: 14px; color: #111827;">New suppressions</td>
    <td style="padding: 12px 16px; text-align: left; border-bottom: 1px solid #eceef2; font-size: 14px; color: #111827; text-align: right; color: #d97706; font-weight: 600;">{{ .SuppressionCount }}</td>
  </tr>
</table>

<p style="margin: 0 0 16px;">High bounce rates can damage your sender reputation. Review your recipient lists and remove invalid or unengaged addresses.</p>

{{ if .AppURL }}
<table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" border="0" align="center" style="margin: 28px auto;">
  <tr><td align="center" bgcolor="#7c3aed" style="border-radius: 8px;">
    <a href="{{ .AppURL }}/bounces" class="btn" style="display: inline-block; padding: 13px 30px; background-color: #7c3aed; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1;">Review bounces</a>
  </td></tr>
</table>
{{ end }}
{{ end }}
